msgctxt "sn56.53:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.53:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "6. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.53:0.3"
msgid "53. Paṭhamasambhejjasutta "
msgstr "53. Where the Waters Flow Together (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.461, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.53:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, yatthimā mahānadiyo saṃsandanti samenti, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are places where the great rivers—the Ganges, Yamuna, Aciravatī, Sarabhū, and Mahī—come together and converge. "

msgctxt "sn56.53:1.2"
msgid "gaṅgā, yamunā, aciravatī, sarabhū, mahī, tato puriso dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni uddhareyya. "
msgstr "Suppose a person was to draw two or three drops of water from such a place. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.53:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.53:1.4"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni, yaṃ vā sambhejjaudakan”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the two or three drops drawn out or the water in the confluence?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.53:1.5"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—saṃbhejjaudakaṃ; appamattakāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatāni. "
msgstr "“Sir, the water in the confluence is certainly more. The two or three drops drawn out are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.53:1.6"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti saṃbhejjaudakaṃ upanidhāya dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni ubbhatānī”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the water in the confluence, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.53:1.7"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.53:1.8"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.53:1.9"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

